Traveller 
Life is filled with roads, diverging and intersecting. Each choice leading you down a path, on a journey, the future unbeknownst to you. 
Yet we travel even when we hope to still ourselves body, mind and spirit life drags us on. Forward we move, willing or unwilling we move, we move because to be alive is to constantly be in motion, thinking, feeling, hurting, achieving.

So go forth traveller, explore your mind, body, spirit, explore this world and explore your future, for YOU HAVE the potential, YOU HAVE the ability, YOU HAVE WHAT IT TAKES!! #loveyourself #love #poem #business #life #me #followme #southafrica #capetown #durban #pietermaritzburg #epic #businessman #businesswoman #today #move #think #qoutes #live
